ActPublic Service Staff Relations Act
PrecisRe-appointment of DAN QUIGLEY of Ottawa, Ontario, to be a full-time member of the Public Service Staff Relations Board to hold office during good behaviour for a period of three years; and order that DAN QUIGLEY shall be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act; effective November 19, 2003.
